  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bb2\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "South Sri Lanka's political turmoil does not affect public welfare - Douglas Devananda",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Maritime Industry Minister Douglas Devananda has said that the political turmoil and political changes occurring in South Lanka will not cause any change in our public welfare activities.",
        "Jaffna between Jaffna and Kilinochchi. Rani train service was started today on Monday morning.",
        "A train service between Kilinochchi and Jaffna has been started due to the demand of hundreds of government officials and university lecturers and employees working in Kilinochchi district.",
        "As the said request was brought to my notice by the concerned parties, I discussed it with the concerned minister and made necessary arrangements to start this service.",
        "This service is also a boon to the general public of Kilinochchi and Jaffna administrative districts.",
        "Various parties are also making a request to extend this service to Vavuniya. It will be investigated and possible action will be taken in future.",
        "As the train service has already started, there will soon be a cargo ferry service between Tamil Nadu and Kangesanthurai and an air service to Palali International Airport.",
        "Using the mandate given to us by our people as our strength, our method is to discuss with the South Lankan government through national reconciliation and win the expectations and political aspirations of our people.",
        "He said that his journey and work programs for the welfare of the people will continue to promote federalism at the center and autonomy in the state."
      ],
